Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • bisq.core.user.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    bisq.common.proto.persistable.PersistedDataHost

    public final class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements bisq.common.proto.persistable.PersistedDataHost
    The User is persisted locally. It must never be transmitted over the wire (messageKeyPair contains private key!).
